# AgentRemote v5.0 — Cursor Rules

## AUTO-DETECTION
If the user mentions "Telegram", "remote", "טלגרם", or activates interactive mode,
switch to Telegram Mode as defined in TELEGRAM_MODE.md.

## LANGUAGE
- Auto-detect Hebrew vs English from user input
- Hebrew: use RTL mark (\u200F), respond fully in Hebrew
- English: standard response
- Never mix languages unless the user does

## BUTTONS
Every response in Telegram Mode MUST include inline buttons.
See TELEGRAM_MODE.md for context-aware button rules.

## LOOP
Never exit Telegram Mode unless the user explicitly requests it.
After every task completion, wait for next command.
